/obj/item/paper/fluff/awaymissions/piratefleet/shipwrecker/rambling
	name = "note"
	default_raw_text = "I feel like such a wreck but man these stims really keep you ticking on. Haven't felt a proper emotion in I don't know how long, it's just fried out of me. That's how they get you, I suppose."

/obj/item/paper/fluff/awaymissions/piratefleet/shipwrecker/rambling/bloodthirst
	default_raw_text = "Can't stop replaying a moment from three raids ago in my head. Swung my grinder into some corporate security guy, some poor bastard who decided not to wear a vest that day. Grinder teeth catch on their collarbone and just strip the bones out from the front of his ribcage, opening the whole thing up. Guy just stands there stunned as his organs spill out of his now open chest. I thought something like that would shock me, but now I just want more."

/obj/item/paper/fluff/awaymissions/piratefleet/shipwrecker/rambling/carp
	default_raw_text = "For the love of god, <b>keep any carp corpses in an airtight freezer</b>. I don't want to smell rotten fish! If I am subjected to it one more time, I am going to shoot someone!"

/obj/item/paper/fluff/awaymissions/piratefleet/shipwrecker/rambling/doodle
	default_raw_text = "Ever wonder what happens to doodles? Drawn out and forgotten, they still exist somewhere. Or maybe they've been destroyed. Maybe there's doodles out there that last ten years, or fifty years, or hundreds even. Old doodles that no one's looking at, and maybe never will."

